  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want my signing phrase to be secure, so that I am safe from phishers.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n1. How do we generate it? Is our RNG secure?\r\n2. How do we secure the stored signing phrase? \r\n3. Is realm db safe from access by other apps?\r\n4. ~Do we actually need it in plain text for the workflow to work?~ yes,we do\r\n\r\nRe 1 - We can consider this one: [react-native-randombytes](https://www.npmjs.com/package/react-native-randombytes)\r\n\r\n",
